column2: responses$`9. Which emerging technology has been the most useful to you`
"I'm not sure what \"emerging technology\" refers to."
"Machine Learning Algorithms that help recommend the next Netflix show I should watch based on my interests."

"Smart speakers have been the most useful emerging tachnology because it allows me to multi task more efficiently. It allows me to browse the web in a sense, look up references, check out current events, shop or call a cab and provide entertainment just by voice commands allowing to also other tasks at the same time."
"I am not a consumer of emerging technologies, although I enjoy researching them and reading about how to regulate their usage."
"Drones (I don't own any drone but I think drones can do things that are physically difficult to humans)"
"the increasing sophistication of web search algorithms"
